{"id": "ChIJV9oX_IHBwoAR9uAjhjusNPk", "rating": 4.4, "userRatingCount": 150, "displayName": {"text": "Fondry", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJV9oX_IHBwoAR9uAjhjusNPk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWelMzWXhORVJ6WDFSU04zcEljRXBUZVdkcWEwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "The service here is great! The line moves fairly quickly as well. I came here particularly to try their weekend special, which at the time was a chorizo mashed potato quiche, but they didn’t have it the Sunday that I came, so I got a couple pastries instead. I got their banana chocolate cruffin and kouignn amaan, the flavors were okay but the pastry themselves you can tell have great attention to detail put into them. Truly Devine lamination and baking. Their matcha was great too!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The service here is great! The line moves fairly quickly as well. I came here particularly to try their weekend special, which at the time was a chorizo mashed potato quiche, but they didn’t have it the Sunday that I came, so I got a couple pastries instead. I got their banana chocolate cruffin and kouignn amaan, the flavors were okay but the pastry themselves you can tell have great attention to detail put into them. Truly Devine lamination and baking. Their matcha was great too!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "internetbethany", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107980623678634571006/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWU9ykfCZuCro0uFvIMkwx13u4SMjgqmE0ymXlPgw2Wi4A4GGc=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-11T17:34:45.173987504Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWelMzWXhORVJ6WDFSU04zcEljRXBUZVdkcWEwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tWelMzWXhORVJ6WDFSU04zcEljRXBUZVdkcWEwRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c181fc17da57:0xf934ac3b8623e0f6"}, {"name": "places/ChIJV9oX_IHBwoAR9uAjhjusNPk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tReVFUaGpXbFIxWWxCT2NDMHRNVTU0U0ZJeE4yYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Fondry is popular for good reason.\n\nEach pastry is so intentionally crafted. The flavours all work together in harmony, and the laminated pastries have some of the most perfect texture. The prices reflect the quality though. These are not cheap pastries, even for LA standards. Overall, highly recommend! Some of the best croissants and pastries in LA.\n\nArrived around 11:30 am on a Saturday (Coachella weekend lol) and still many pastries available.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Fondry is popular for good reason.\n\nEach pastry is so intentionally crafted. The flavours all work together in harmony, and the laminated pastries have some of the most perfect texture. The prices reflect the quality though. These are not cheap pastries, even for LA standards. Overall, highly recommend! Some of the best croissants and pastries in LA.\n\nArrived around 11:30 am on a Saturday (Coachella weekend lol) and still many pastries available.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "David Li", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112391684107063049159/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUW3drrzmkclXCnMjsjZCIGLOWdVafPs2fNi6jthw-8mnUIGBEh=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-19T05:52:42.999493536Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tReVFUaGpXbFIxWWxCT2NDMHRNVTU0U0ZJeE4yYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tReVFUaGpXbFIxWWxCT2NDMHRNVTU0U0ZJeE4yYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c181fc17da57:0xf934ac3b8623e0f6"}, {"name": "places/ChIJV9oX_IHBwoAR9uAjhjusNPk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xab1VFUnNVRTlIVWtGZmRXRlRaVWRGYld0UFFrRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Pastry and drinks were amazing, we particularly loved the mushroom bechamel Danish pastry.\n\nWe came here 9am on a Sunday, and there was already a queue before it opened. Very limited parking space that gets full quickly, but you can park by the street for free.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Pastry and drinks were amazing, we particularly loved the mushroom bechamel Danish pastry.\n\nWe came here 9am on a Sunday, and there was already a queue before it opened. Very limited parking space that gets full quickly, but you can park by the street for free.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Steven Ho", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110390705346543450663/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL4bo5D5n8jDFe0ji2NH7VjTv0pxJ-hnoACqobMWvXlrnM4NQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-13T11:23:47.410649117Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xab1VFUnNVRTlIVWtGZmRXRlRaVWRGYld0UFFrRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xab1VFUnNVRTlIVWtGZmRXRlRaVWRGYld0UFFrRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c181fc17da57:0xf934ac3b8623e0f6"}, {"name": "places/ChIJV9oX_IHBwoAR9uAjhjusNPk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsYVdqWjBNbVp6TWpRMGRsOWhjVVk1ZWtOTWQzYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Came to try their pastries as it’s shared to be unique which is true, flavors is assorted and was told they switch up the flavors once in a while.\n\nCame to try their mushroom pastry and it was pretty good except if it could be heated up prior to chowing it down would be so idea\n\nParking is limited despite their shared community parking circle with other vendors so look for street parking", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Came to try their pastries as it’s shared to be unique which is true, flavors is assorted and was told they switch up the flavors once in a while.\n\nCame to try their mushroom pastry and it was pretty good except if it could be heated up prior to chowing it down would be so idea\n\nParking is limited despite their shared community parking circle with other vendors so look for street parking", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Nat awee", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102578254044803169485/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPstE8Qxo-urbjgSg6uX4MjFlf36Ik_I-o-kse7vrBq-hHtzaqdA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-06T18:08:36.527336742Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsYVdqWjBNbVp6TWpRMGRsOWhjVVk1ZWtOTWQzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tsYVdqWjBNbVp6TWpRMGRsOWhjVVk1ZWtOTWQzYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c181fc17da57:0xf934ac3b8623e0f6"}, {"name": "places/ChIJV9oX_IHBwoAR9uAjhjusNPk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tvM1QzZExWazFZWWxaZlNXVjZYMnQzYkVSaVJtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Did anyone say Croissant? Their pastries are yummy, drinks are great, the vibe is chill. Parking can be challenging and the line could get long, but if this place wasn't great, then there wouldn't be any of these lines. Enjoy the waiting game, but if you get lucky, line can go fast and parking can get easy.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Did anyone say Croissant? Their pastries are yummy, drinks are great, the vibe is chill. Parking can be challenging and the line could get long, but if this place wasn't great, then there wouldn't be any of these lines. Enjoy the waiting game, but if you get lucky, line can go fast 